&lt;div class="code"&gt;&lt;pre class="code text"&gt;&lt;a id="rest_code_a15b991e6be941f7bc0c1a54d8ea3b81-1" name="rest_code_a15b991e6be941f7bc0c1a54d8ea3b81-1" href="https://tkurtbond.github.io/posts/2022/02/05/redimensioning-formal-parameter-arrays-in-openvms-basic-revisited/#rest_code_a15b991e6be941f7bc0c1a54d8ea3b81-1"&gt;&lt;/a&gt;%BAS-F-PROLOSSOR, Internal error in VAX BASIC Run-Time Library.  Please submit an SPR
&lt;a id="rest_code_a15b991e6be941f7bc0c1a54d8ea3b81-2" name="rest_code_a15b991e6be941f7bc0c1a54d8ea3b81-2" href="https://tkurtbond.github.io/posts/2022/02/05/redimensioning-formal-parameter-arrays-in-openvms-basic-revisited/#rest_code_a15b991e6be941f7bc0c1a54d8ea3b81-2"&gt;&lt;/a&gt;-BAS-I-FROFUN, In external function ALT_REDIM
